 419               	***************************************************************
 420               	*** HUD panel (window plane, right side)
 421               	***************************************************************
 422               	
 423               	* panel layout (rows 0..27 of 6 cells):
 424               	*  0 "1UP"  1 p1 score   3 "HI"  4 hi score   6 "2UP"  7 p2 score
 425               	*  20 "A" + area   24 "CR" + credits   26 lives icons
 426               	* The panel uses its own pre-rendered opaque glyph tiles (PANEL_TILE..)
 427               	* so it never competes with the in-field fg cache.
 428               	
